* Wireless Controller
* Detachable hard drive <small>(instead of memory card; initially 20 GB, 60 GB after August 2008)</small>
* [[Ethernet]] cable
* Wired headset
* [[Component video|Component]]/[[Composite video|Composite]] Hybrid HD AV cable with integrated [[TOSLINK]] output port

