* [[Compact Flash]], [[Secure Digital]], and [[Memory Stick]] [[Flash card]] readers
* Software-based backwards compatibility with [[PlayStation 2|PS2]] and [[PlayStation|PS1]]  games in [[PAL region]] models
* Hardware-based backwards compatibility with [[PlayStation 2|PS2]] and [[PlayStation|PS1]]  games in [[NTSC|NTSC region]] models

'''80 GB (old):'''

* Includes everything in the 60 GB plus:
* Software-based backwards compatibility with [[PlayStation 2|PS2]] and [[PlayStation|PS1]] games

'''80 GB (new):'''

* Includes everything in the 40 GB plus:
* [[DualShock 3]] instead of [[PlayStation 3 accessories#Sixaxis|Sixaxis]]

'''160 GB:'''

* Includes everything in the 80 GB (new)</div></div>
